---
layout: base.njk
title: Blog | Web Design and SEO Insights for NYC Businesses
description: Read practical articles on web development, SEO, hosting, and AI workflows for law firms and local businesses in NYC.
canonical: https://www.gothamwebdev.com/blog/
pageKey: blog
navRoot: ../
permalink: /blog/index.html
breadcrumbs:
  - label: Home
    href: index.html
  - label: Blog
---
<main>
  <section class="page-hero"><div class="container"><h1>Blog</h1><p>Guides and updates focused on growth, performance, and digital strategy.</p></div></section>

  <section>
    <div class="container cards-grid">
      {% for post in collections.blogPosts %}
        <article class="card">
          <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
          {% if post.data.description %}<p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>{% endif %}
          <p class="section-subtitle">Published {{ post.date | blogDate }}</p>
        </article>
      {% else %}
        <article class="card">
          <h2>New Articles Coming Soon</h2>
          <p>Daily posts are being prepared and will appear here shortly.</p>
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
